text: Aurel Bylykbashi is a member of the Assembly of the Republic of Albania for the Democratic Party of Albania. He joined the assembly after the resignation of 3 members at the 2011 Albanian local elections. ==Footnotes== Category:Living people Category:Democratic Party of Albania politicians Category:Members of the Parliament of Albania Category:21st-century Albanian politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
